race.comment: REGAL ZEUS (3) comes through a decent race at Flemington and although safely held he'll be better suited up to 1600m third up and should park just off the speed. In a race weakened by scratchings he now looks the one to go on top. PRESSER (13) has been racing consistently and got a deserved win last start. Building a good record at this distance and he might go on with it now. EL ROCKO (2) fades out at Flemington last time but has winning claims off his Sale Cup victory prior. FARHH FLUNG (11) only missed by a whisker last start at Flemington and draws to enjoy a soft run.
